        <div class="msgSubject">THM Frustrations.  Any Suggestions?</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-10-04 11:57:26   | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1286215046206261131" id="quote-1286215046206261131" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1286215046206261131" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=179&amp;mid=1286215046206261131&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1286215046206261131&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1286215046206261131" onclick="followToggle('add','1286215046206261131')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
