      <div class="msgContentFrame">Macros seem to be the best bet in my book setup a group of buttons to target: <br /> <br />* /targetpc <br /> <br />Targets the closest PC within a certain radius. <br /> <br />* /targetnpc <br /> <br />Targets the closest NPC or monster within a certain radius.  <br /> <br /> <br />Also can spam a macro with: <br /> <br />/aoe on <br />/action Sacrifice &lt;me&gt; <br />/wait 2.5 <br />/ac &quot;Punishing Barbs&quot; &lt;me&gt; <br />/aoe off <br /> <br />And tank like no tomorrow ;) <br /> <br />Also i would say get conjurer to at least 4 and have 2 cures ready to go allows me to fight much harder mobs and do my quest on extremely hard settings.... <br /> <br /><i><span class="sm">Edited, Oct  4th 2010  3:25pm by kenshynOnShiva </span></i><div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div>....::: 90 Blue Mage :::....  <br />90Sam/ 85War/ 85Dnc / 85DRK/ 90SMN/  85PUP/ 90SCH/ 56Nin/ 62Rng/ 50Thf/ 51drg/49 whm/45 Rdm <br />Genbu [O] Suzaku [O] Seiryu [O] Byakko [O] Kirin [O] In Loving Memory of Kirin RIP 3/6/05  <br /><a href="HTTP://eknightsonshiva.proboards28.com" rel="external nofollow" title="eknightsonshiva.proboards28.com">xXIEOSIXx Forums on Shiva</a> <br /> <br /> <br /><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/340581.png" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /></div></div>
